<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.9">
<l>kaṇṇārkaṇ ṇapuram kaṭikai kaṭikamaḻum</l>
<l>taṇṇārtā maraicūḻ talaiccaṅ kamēlticaiyuḷ</l>
<l>viṇṇōrnāṇ matiyai virikiṉ ṟaveñcuṭarai</l>
<l>kaṇṇārakkaṇ ṭukoṇṭu kaḷikkiṉṟatiṅ keṉṟukolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When will be the ecstasy, having seen for myself,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that my eyes are filled,</l>
<l>The [one who is] daily moon to the celestials, the warm radiating sun</l>
<l>Here in the western region in Talaiccaṅkam, encircled by cool lotuses</l>
<l rend="indent">which waft fragrance,</l>
<l>[In] Kaṇṇapuram which fills the eyes, [and in] Kaṭikai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
